[{"ave_id":"AVE-2004-0007","file_name":"2004/AVE-2004-0007.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2004-2687","title":"DistCC 守护进程远程代码执行漏洞","description":"DistCC 分布式编译器守护进程（distccd）存在命令执行漏洞，当服务器未配置访问限制时，远程攻击者可通过向守护进程发送特制的编译任务请求，从而在目标服务器上以守护进程权限执行任意系统命令。该漏洞影响 distcc 2.x 版本（含 XCode 1.5 等集成产品），CVSS 评分 9.3，危害等级严重。建议配置访问控制列表或使用 SSH 加密模式修复。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.3,"aliases":["CVE-2004-2687"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2004-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T22:10:08.157","remediation":"配置 distccd 的 `--allow` 参数仅允许受信 IP 段（如 `distccd --allow 192.168.1.0/24`），或改用 SSH 加密隧道模式 (`--ssh`) 传输编译任务；在防火墙层面限制 3632 端口的入站访问，仅对编译客户端开放；升级至 distcc 3.0 及以上版本可获得更完善的访问控制机制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2005-03/0183.html","http://distcc.samba.org/security.html","http://lists.samba.org/archive/distcc/2004q3/002550.html","http://lists.samba.org/archive/distcc/2004q3/002562.html","http://www.metasploit.org/projects/Framework/exploits.html#distcc_exec","http://www.osvdb.org/13378","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/9915","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/network/cves/2004/CVE-2004-2687.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2004/CVE-2004-2687.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/PoC-in-GitHub/blob/a8dd65f3bd9f09f4c40ddbec294c8d30c1b24bd7/2004/CVE-2004-2687.json","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/69a5a3cf926251a00061ec14d208b227367df73d/network/cves/2004/CVE-2004-2687.yaml","https://github.com/arschlochnop/VulnWatchdog/blob/461e9fce2382e9802c4bb94efd2da8b5153bbbe3/data/2004/CVE-2004-2687-k4miyo_CVE-2004-2687.md","https://github.com/rix4uni/cvemapping/blob/72a822f4866721f573938ebc544bcc94c22a338d/2004/CVE-2004-2687/exploit.py","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2004/CVE-2004-2687","https://github.com/HackTricks-wiki/hacktricks/blob/93cd73b85df95ce61853ae639be6d25e8cf3eeb6/src/network-services-pentesting/3632-pentesting-distcc.md","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2004-2687_3.yaml","https://github.com/ycdxsb/PocOrExp_in_Github/blob/4fbd60af032aab6c0dd5800ec5f5834d73216d1f/2004/README.md","https://github.com/sari3l/Poc-Monitor/blob/372603f08cfb4e5ff7a25a1c0e01dd52b610397e/2004/CVE-2004-2687.json","https://github.com/h3x0v3rl0rd/distccd_rce_CVE-2004-2687","https://github.com/k4miyo/CVE-2004-2687","https://github.com/angelpimentell/distcc_cve_2004-2687_exploit","https://github.com/micheaol/distccd_rce_CVE-2004-2687","https://github.com/nulltrace1336/Metasploitable-2-Distcc-Exploit-via-Kali-Linux-CVE-2004-2687"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2004/AVE-2004-0007.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2004-0006","file_name":"2004/AVE-2004-0006.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2004-1965","title":"Open Bulletin Board (OpenBB) 1.0.6 及之前版本跨站脚本漏洞","description":"Open Bulletin Board (OpenBB) 1.0.6 及更早版本中存在多个跨站脚本（XSS）漏洞，由于未对用户输入进行充分过滤，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向 member.php 的 redirect 参数、myhome.php 的 to 参数、post.php 的 TID 参数或 index.php 的 redirect 参数注入恶意 Web 脚本或 HTML 代码，在受害者浏览器中执行任意脚本，窃取会话 Cookie 或进行钓鱼攻击，影响系统机密性。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.3,"aliases":["CVE-2004-1965"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2004-04-25T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T22:08:44.267","remediation":"升级 OpenBB 至 1.0.6 以上版本，该版本已修复多个 XSS 注入点。对所有用户输入参数（member.php 的 redirect、myhome.php 的 to、post.php 的 TID 等）进行 HTML 实体编码输出，在应用层面禁用不安全的重定向功能或添加白名单验证机制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=108301983206107&w=2","http://secunia.com/advisories/11481","http://securitytracker.com/id?1009935","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/10214","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/15966","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/43811","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2004/CVE-2004-1965.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2004/CVE-2004-1965.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/a5c2e8e4dab8c8e618ba76807c3e07587b7d781a/http/cves/2004/CVE-2004-1965.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d5838f491a2d04e9f823fb9638e9e6f0b038d399/cves/2004/1xxx/CVE-2004-1965.json","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/2004/CVE-2004-1965.rules","https://github.com/hack007x/veil_poc/blob/5cfe1da6e975ba816d728597885a5c5e79bda8bd/cves/2004/CVE-2004-1965.poc","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/05ddc188299e518fc74cdc1a27862f35b96b23b2/2004/CVE-2004-1965.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2004/CVE-2004-1965","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2004-1965_45.yaml","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2004/CVE-2004-1965.json","https://github.com/brenonevs/prs-pentest/blob/001cf17eedeb4aad73618d3140ca1f5dc93e69b3/CVEs%20&%20POCs/2004/CVE-2004-1965.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2004/AVE-2004-0006.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2004-0005","file_name":"2004/AVE-2004-0005.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2004-1641","title":"Titan FTP Server 长命令堆溢出漏洞","description":"Titan FTP Server 3.21 及更早版本存在基于堆的缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标服务器发送特制的长 FTP 命令（如 CWD、STAT、LIST），触发堆缓冲区溢出，导致服务进程崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Titan FTP Server 3.21 及之前版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。建议用户升级至最新版本以修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2004-1641"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2004-08-29T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T22:08:06.133","remediation":"立即将 Titan FTP Server 升级至 3.22 或更高版本（该漏洞在后续版本中已修复）。如当前仍在运行已停产的旧版 Titan FTP Server，建议迁移至 South River Technologies 当前支持的 Titan MFT 或 Titan SFTP Server 产品线。若无法立即升级，可在防火墙或 IPS 设备上配置规则，拦截超长 FTP 命令（CWD/STAT/LIST 参数超过 20480 字节），并限制匿名用户访问权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=109396159332523&w=2","http://secunia.com/advisories/12419","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/11069","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/17172","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/426","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/network/cves/2004/CVE-2004-1641.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2004/CVE-2004-1641.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/a5c2e8e4dab8c8e618ba76807c3e07587b7d781a/network/cves/2004/CVE-2004-1641.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d5838f491a2d04e9f823fb9638e9e6f0b038d399/cves/2004/1xxx/CVE-2004-1641.json","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2004-1641_7.yaml","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/23b9072d94002e85c65869c9b10a30b4a0f4057c/CVE/data/2004/CVE-2004-1641.json","https://github.com/0xMarcio/cve/blob/a209ce815e26f65fdf4e0d916680102a59565542/2004/CVE-2004-1641.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/bfc71abcad51f07aa63bd81da281ee9359b3b3bf/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pfgr-89g7-q7q8/GHSA-pfgr-89g7-q7q8.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/titan_ftp_heap_overflow.nasl","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2008/CVE-2008-0702","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-2008-0702.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2004/AVE-2004-0005.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2004-0004","file_name":"2004/AVE-2004-0004.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2004-1602","title":"ProFTPD 1.2.x 远程用户枚举漏洞","description":"ProFTPd 1.2.x（包括 1.2.8 及 1.2.10 版本）存在用户枚举漏洞。由于服务器在处理有效用户名和无效用户名的登录请求时响应时间存在差异，未经认证的远程攻击者可通过计时攻击逐一向服务器发送登录请求并测量响应延迟，从而枚举出系统上的有效用户账户。该漏洞虽不直接导致代码执行，但可为后续暴力破解或针对性攻击提供信息基础，影响运行 ProFTPd 1.2.x 的所有 Linux/Unix 系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2004-1602"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2004-10-15T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T22:08:01.587","remediation":"升级 ProFTPD 至 1.3.0 或更高版本（当前最新为 1.3.10），该版本统一了 USER 命令对有效和无效用户的响应时间，消除时序侧信道。若无法升级，可在防火墙限制 FTP 端口仅允许可信 IP 访问，并配置 MaxLoginAttempts 限制暴力枚举。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=109786760926133&w=2","http://security.lss.hr/index.php?page=details&ID=LSS-2004-10-02","http://securitytracker.com/id?1011687","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/11430","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/17724","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/581","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/network/cves/2004/CVE-2004-1602.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2004/CVE-2004-1602.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/a5c2e8e4dab8c8e618ba76807c3e07587b7d781a/network/cves/2004/CVE-2004-1602.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d5838f491a2d04e9f823fb9638e9e6f0b038d399/cves/2004/1xxx/CVE-2004-1602.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2004/CVE-2004-1602","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/23b9072d94002e85c65869c9b10a30b4a0f4057c/CVE/data/2004/CVE-2004-1602.json","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2004-1602.yaml","https://github.com/b1ank1108/VulSentinel/blob/73c794f6d98539e5acdaf98b3ca4de1832c6f13b/reports/network/cves/2004/CVE-2004-1602.md","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/pre2008/proftpd_user_enum.nasl","https://github.com/RogoLabs/consensus-engine/blob/c8cb8d393cb233bc0222f12dee382f3879140c3d/docs/data/2004/CVE-2004-1602.json","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/CVE-2004-1602.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2004/AVE-2004-0004.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2004-0003","file_name":"2004/AVE-2004-0003.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2004-0656","title":"PureFTPd accept_client 函数拒绝服务漏洞","description":"PureFTPd 1.0.18 及更早版本中的 accept_client 函数存在连接数限制缺陷，远程攻击者可通过建立大量并发连接超出服务器最大连接数限制，导致 FTP 服务耗尽系统资源而拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 PureFTPd 1.0.18 及此前所有版本，攻击者无需认证即可利用，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。建议升级至 PureFTPd 1.0.19 及以上版本修复。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2004-0656"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2004-08-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T22:06:06.270","remediation":"升级 PureFTPd 至 1.0.19 或更高版本。如无法立即升级，可在配置文件中调低 `MaxClientsNumber` 和 `MaxClientsPerIP` 参数以限制最大连接数，同时使用防火墙（如 iptables）限制单 IP 并发连接数作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.gentoo.org/security/en/glsa/glsa-200407-04.xml","http://www.pureftpd.org/","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/16611","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/network/cves/2004/CVE-2004-0656.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2004/CVE-2004-0656.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/a5c2e8e4dab8c8e618ba76807c3e07587b7d781a/network/cves/2004/CVE-2004-0656.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d5838f491a2d04e9f823fb9638e9e6f0b038d399/cves/2004/0xxx/CVE-2004-0656.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2004/CVE-2004-0656","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/23b9072d94002e85c65869c9b10a30b4a0f4057c/CVE/data/2004/CVE-2004-0656.json","https://github.com/Terry-ten/AI-POC/blob/62e60c784027e40d64b94669324ee032f1659f14/pocs/nuclei/network/cves/2004/CVE-2004-0656.yaml","https://github.com/MaineK00n/vuln-data/blob/9e1ff46005584f5d4c094bd8d97e510415b9f767/goval-dictionary/debian/11/CVE-2004-0656.json","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2004-0656_7.yaml","https://github.com/Kuduxaaa/hunting-knowledge-base/blob/e9de2ea715300eb67318e21f3930704d36ad8d2b/signatures/nuclei/network/cves/2004/CVE-2004-0656.yaml","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/G/gentoo_GLSA-200407-04.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2004/AVE-2004-0003.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2004-0002","file_name":"2004/AVE-2004-0002.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2004-0519","title":"SquirrelMail 1.4.x 跨站脚本漏洞","description":"SquirrelMail 1.4.2 存在多个跨站脚本（XSS）漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向 compose.php 等页面的 mailbox 参数等多个攻击向量注入恶意脚本代码。当其他用户访问特制链接时，恶意脚本将在用户浏览器中执行，导致攻击者可窃取用户认证信息或冒充用户执行任意操作。该漏洞影响 SquirrelMail 1.4.2 及之前版本，CVSS 评分 6.8，危害等级中危。建议升级至 SquirrelMail 1.4.3 或更高版本修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.8,"aliases":["CVE-2004-0519"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2004-08-18T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T22:05:48.060","remediation":"升级至 SquirrelMail 1.4.3a 或更高版本（1.4.2 及之前版本受影响）。Red Hat 用户可通过 RHSA-2004:240 更新至 1.4.3a，Debian 用户通过 DSA-535 更新，Gentoo 用户升级至 >=mail-client/squirrelmail-1.4.3_rc1。如无法升级，可在 php.ini 中关闭 register_globals 以降低攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://distro.conectiva.com.br/atualizacoes/?id=a&anuncio=000858","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=108334862800260","http://rhn.redhat.com/errata/RHSA-2004-240.html","http://secunia.com/advisories/11531","http://secunia.com/advisories/11686","http://secunia.com/advisories/11870","http://secunia.com/advisories/12289","http://security.gentoo.org/glsa/glsa-200405-16.xml","http://www.debian.org/security/2004/dsa-535","http://www.novell.com/linux/security/advisories/2005_19_sr.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/advisories/6827","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/361857","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/10246","https://bugzilla.fedora.us/show_bug.cgi?id=1733","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/16025","https://oval.cisecurity.org/repository/search/definition/oval%3Aorg.mitre.oval%3Adef%3A1006","https://oval.cisecurity.org/repository/search/definition/oval%3Aorg.mitre.oval%3Adef%3A10274","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/24068","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2004/CVE-2004-0519.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2004/CVE-2004-0519.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/a5c2e8e4dab8c8e618ba76807c3e07587b7d781a/http/cves/2004/CVE-2004-0519.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/medium/cve-2004-0519-1306.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2004-0519.js","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2004/CVE-2004-0519.json","https://github.com/DefectDojo/django-DefectDojo/blob/619e5656f308396a3cc3a7f039c6426ae98baa17/dojo/tools/nuclei/parser.py","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/Z/z-11753.yaml","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x11000/10246/info.html","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/cve-2004-0519.yaml","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2004-0519_3.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2004/AVE-2004-0002.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2004-0001","file_name":"2004/AVE-2004-0001.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2004-0437","title":"Titan FTP Server 3.0 LIST命令拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Titan FTP Server 3.01 build 163 及更早版本（build 169 之前）在处理 LIST -L 命令时存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程认证用户在执行 LIST -L 命令过程中主动断开连接，触发服务器访问已关闭的无效套接字，导致 FTP 服务进程崩溃。攻击者需持有合法账户才能利用，攻击复杂度较低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2004-0437"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2004-07-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T22:05:38.700","remediation":"升级 Titan FTP Server 至 3.10 build 169 或更高版本。如无法立即升级，可在防火墙或 FTP 服务端限制可登录用户范围，仅允许可信 IP 连接，降低被利用风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/vulnwatch/2004-q2/0025.html","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=108378048513596&w=2","http://www.securiteam.com/windowsntfocus/5RP0215CUU.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/16057","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/24080","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/network/cves/2004/CVE-2004-0437.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2004/CVE-2004-0437.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/a5c2e8e4dab8c8e618ba76807c3e07587b7d781a/network/cves/2004/CVE-2004-0437.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d5838f491a2d04e9f823fb9638e9e6f0b038d399/cves/2004/0xxx/CVE-2004-0437.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2004/CVE-2004-0437","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/23b9072d94002e85c65869c9b10a30b4a0f4057c/CVE/data/2004/CVE-2004-0437.json","https://github.com/mabitosk